{{SupportPage|vendor=Belkin|vs_id_old=386}} "141400520027J REV:0A" is silkscreened on the board. The default SSID is (maybe, unknown status fresh from the factory) '''Belkin_G_Wireless_XXXXXX''' where '''XXXXXX''' is the last 3 octets of the WLAN MAC address (w/ uppercase letters). When reset via the reset button, the device will take the SSID of '''Belkin_G_Wireless_''' with no trailing characters. Resetting by way of the web configuration interface resets the SSID to the three octets included format.
